# NEMETIC STRING
# AI_Chatbot_Therapy (C187)

Φ(AI_Chatbot_Therapy) = σ(access|intimacy) ∘ ρ(empathy|algorithm) ∘ λ(immediacy|depth) ∘ β(bridge|chasm) ∘ δγ(virtual|embodied) ∘ μ(cost|value) + ε | :liminal

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(access|intimacy)      :: Air  :: Immediate access to therapeutic dialogue but cannot achieve genuine intimate connection
# ρ(empathy|algorithm)    :: Water :: Simulated empathy flows through algorithmic patterns lacking authentic resonance
# λ(immediacy|depth)      :: Fire  :: 24/7 availability provides instant support yet burns shallow without therapeutic depth
# β(bridge|chasm)         :: Wood  :: Serves as bridge to mental health care while widening chasm of human disconnection
# δγ(virtual|embodied)    :: Earth :: Virtual presence cannot replicate embodied therapeutic relationship
# μ(cost|value)           :: Metal :: Reduced cost increases accessibility but may devalue the therapeutic alliance
